194
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,000
Pi Pi!

195
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:39,500
Jia Lin! Vyľakal si ma!

196
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:41,290
Poďme sa najesť.

197
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,130
