- Áno?

384
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:15,500
Nepochopili ste ma.

385
00:25:15,500 --> 00:25:16,590
Nie som žobrák.

386
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:19,290
Len som chcel, aby ste mi 
ukázali cestu k metru.

387
00:25:21,090 --> 00:25:22,200
Och...

388
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,090
Prepáčte.

389
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,590
Vezmem vás tam.

390
00:25:28,590 --> 00:25:29,950
Ukážte, chytím vás za ruku.

391
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,200
Pozor na schody.

392
00:25:52,790 --> 00:25:56,000
Hej! Zlodej! Ukradol mi peňaženku! Zlodej!

393
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:59,400
Hej! Hej! Stoj!

394
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:01,000
Vráť mi moju peňaženku!

395
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,400
Stoj!

396
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:08,000
- Stoj!
- Môj moped!

397
00:26:14,290 --> 00:26:15,290
Nastúpte!

398
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:27,790
Spomaľte!

399
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:36,790
Povraciam sa.

400
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:43,700
Dopekla! Kuan Yong, chyťme ho!

401
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,790
Dostali sme sa do hry.

402
00:26:56,090 --> 00:26:58,290
Nevadí to, ak budete takto jazdiť?

403
00:26:58,290 --> 00:26:59,590
<i>Nebojte sa.</i>

404
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:08,290
Hej, predbehni toho červeného.

405
00:27:10,590 --> 00:27:11,590
Ani náhodou!

406
00:27:17,090 --> 00:27:18,400
Dupni na to a predbehni ho!

407
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,590
<i>Dokážeš to?</i>

408
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:35,000
Čo sa deje?

409
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:56,200
Koho chytíme s tvojím 
biednym šoférovaním?

410
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:58,760
Kašlite na moju peňaženku.

411
00:27:58,760 --> 00:28:00,000
Choď tadiaľ.

412
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,500
Máš biedny vkus na muziku.

413
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:08,200
Ty si proste len zlý šofér.

414
00:28:09,090 --> 00:28:10,090
Tak šoféruj ty.

415
00:28:10,090 --> 00:28:11,290
Dobre, budem.

416
00:28:15,790 --> 00:28:18,000
Tvoj zadok. Schudni! 
Máš zadok ako nákladiak.

417
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:19,500
Nebojte sa. Bude to v poriadku.

418
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:33,790
Nie je to príliš nahlas?

419
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:35,590
Toto je skutočná muzika.

420
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:46,900
Áno!

421
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,290
Sledujte a učte sa.

422
00:29:16,290 --> 00:29:18,900
- Mal by si viac počúvať modernú hudbu.
- Čo ty vieš?

423
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:21,000
Počúvam len klasiku.

424
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:23,400
Mne sa páči pop. Ty počúvaš stariny.

425
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:25,200
- Kto to vôbec počúva.
- Ja.

426
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:27,000
Áno! Lebo si fosília.

427
00:29:33,900 --> 00:29:35,000
Mal pravdu.

428
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:39,000
<i>Pozor! Pozor!</i>

429
00:29:58,590 --> 00:30:00,900
<i>Hej! Ah!</i>

430
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:26,700
Nazdar!

431
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,700
Ideme za ním?

432
00:31:03,700 --> 00:31:05,900
Slečna Guan, máte tam všetko?

433
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:11,500
100... 200... 300...

434
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:14,650
Presne 600. Je to všetko.

435
00:31:16,290 --> 00:31:18,090
Aj doklady tu mám všetky.

436
00:31:18,090 --> 00:31:19,200
Ďakujem.

437
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,500
Ďakujem.

438
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,290
Tak ja pôjdem...

439
00:31:24,700 --> 00:31:25,700
Počkať.

440
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:32,290
Ak sa niekedy dostanete do problémov...

441
00:31:32,290 --> 00:31:33,900
Môžete mi zavolať.

442
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,500
Ďakujem.

443
00:31:39,590 --> 00:31:40,840
Ďakujem. Ďakujem.

444
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:46,450
Mám ju sledovať?

445
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:48,900
Netreba.

446
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:51,900
Tak poďme.

447
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,590
Máme zničené auto.

448
00:31:55,090 --> 00:31:57,200
Dnes je celkom pekne. Prejdime sa.

449
00:31:58,090 --> 00:32:00,000
Nemali sme ťa pustiť za volant.

